NexoraPlayer is designed only to play multimedia files stored locally on your device. It is strictly prohibited to:
• Play, distribute or store content that infringes copyright.
• Use the application for illegal purposes or in violation of your country’s laws.
• Try to modify, decompile or reverse engineer the application code.

3. USER CONTENT
All multimedia content you play is your sole responsibility. NexoraPlayer does not store, distribute, monetize or remotely access any of your files. Your library remains completely on your device.

4. ONLINE LYRICS FEATURE
Lyrics search accesses third-party services. This feature is fully optional. We do not guarantee the accuracy, permanent availability or legality of content obtained from external services. Downloaded lyrics must be used respecting the applicable copyright.

5. UPDATES AND CHANGES
The developer may update, modify or discontinue NexoraPlayer at any time without prior notice. Updates may change existing features or add new terms of use.

