    <string name="legal_privacy_text" formatted="false">NEXORAPLAYER PRIVACY POLICY
Last updated: 2025

At NexoraPlayer your privacy is a priority. This policy clearly explains what information is used, how and why.

──────────────────────────────────────
WHAT DATA DO WE COLLECT?
──────────────────────────────────────
NexoraPlayer does NOT collect:
• Name, email, phone number or any personally identifiable data.
• Playback history or song lists.
• Geographic location data.
• Contact information or other installed apps.
• Advertising identifiers or behavior analytics.

──────────────────────────────────────
ACCESS TO DEVICE FILES
──────────────────────────────────────
The application requests storage read permission only to list and play the audio and video files you choose. These files:
• Are never transmitted to external servers.
• Are not shared with third parties.
• Remain fully under your control.

──────────────────────────────────────
ONLINE LYRICS (OPTIONAL)
──────────────────────────────────────
When you manually enable lyrics search, the song title and artist name are sent to third-party services to retrieve results. This means:
• We do not send information to our own servers.
• We do not link these searches to your identity.
• We do not store a history of your lyric searches.
This feature is completely optional and can be disabled at any time from settings.

──────────────────────────────────────
EQUALIZER AND AUDIO
──────────────────────────────────────
The equalizer and all audio processing operate entirely locally on your device. No audio fragment is transmitted to external servers.

──────────────────────────────────────
REQUIRED PERMISSIONS
──────────────────────────────────────
• Read external storage: to access your music and video files.
• Internet (optional): only for lyrics search when enabled.
• Notifications: to show playback controls in the notification bar.
• Foreground service: to keep playback active when the app is minimized.

──────────────────────────────────────
CHANGES TO THIS POLICY
──────────────────────────────────────
Any significant change to this policy will be notified through app updates. By continuing to use NexoraPlayer after an update, you accept the current policy.

──────────────────────────────────────
CONTACT
──────────────────────────────────────
For privacy questions or to exercise your rights:
Telegram: t.me/Gh0stDeveloper
GitHub: github.com/Gh0stDeveloper

